"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        RNGParameters structures with different cryptographic algorithm fields.
        """
a = objects.RNGParameters(cryptographic_algorithm=enums.
    CryptographicAlgorithm.DES)
b = objects.RNGParameters(cryptographic_algorithm=enums.
    CryptographicAlgorithm.AES)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
